        <h3>Chief Financial Officer</h3>
        <p>
            The Chief Financial Officer, with the nickname C.F.O., is the overseer of the Cashbots. He resides within 
            the Cashbot Vault in Cashbot HQ.
        </p>
        <img style="display:block;margin:0 auto;height:225px;width:auto" src="~/images/cogs/cashbots/Chief_Financial_Officer.png" />
        <p>
            After successfully building a cashbot suit disguise and earning a promotion, a toon can the C.F.O. To enter the
            C.F.O. battle, a toon must enter the Cashbot Vault doors (through the giant double doors across the headquarters, 
            shown below). A toon can enter this battle with a maximum of 7 other toons. Once everyone has gone up the elevator, 
            an orange monkey named Mata Hairy will be there. Mata Hairy tries to sneak into the vault but is caught instantly by
            the C.F.O. himself! From there, the toons will have to fight some Cashbots before fighting the C.F.O. The final battle
            against the C.F.O. consists of stomping goons and using giant magnet cranes to throw those goons and safes at the C.F.O.'s head.
            Be careful, the goons light deals more damage as the C.F.O. takes more damage. Upon defeat, toons will celebrate and 
            be rewared with a speedchat unite!
        </p>
        <p>
            Here's a tip: do NOT throw a safe at the C.F.O. unless he is stunned! That will provide him with a helmet that blocks all attacks.
        </p>
